{"tid":2143651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣警元旦受襲申匿名令被拒 官稱早被起底 非匿名令能補救","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T15:07:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd91bd9c79796e45a49edf8f46357b2828da02e2","tid":2143651,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/5JVV2CKUJ7KQSSFWROVMPGIVEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F5JVV2CKUJ7KQSSFWROVMPGIVEY%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=495cb506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F5JVV2CKUJ7KQSSFWROVMPGIVEY%2F&h=a47050c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/5JVV2CKUJ7KQSSFWROVMPGIVEY/</a><br />\n<br />\n今年元旦當晚有示威者在旺角堵路示威，其間有便衣警遇襲，警方事後拘捕四名青年並控以襲警罪。四人否認控罪，案件今進行審前覆核，控方為受襲警申請匿名令，指雖然警員早於去年8月已被起底，但聆訊一旦公開其姓名，擔心會有新一輪的網上攻擊及起底。裁判官則表示，心理報告指受襲警有創傷，卻又毋須臨床關注，故無法確認其精神狀況；況且受襲警的資料早已在公眾領域存在，非匿名令能補救，終拒絕頒下命令。"},{"pid":"258827fd84896402be3aecf3328484dd3d563ab9","tid":2143651,"uid":133,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"有創傷？邊度？個腦呀"},{"pid":"bb7249f2fb2ac4e0633b49b4d4f78ea39e5e945b","tid":2143651,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7106bfbdc2d25ee3bf8fbbb664ec4eb14198022d","tid":2143651,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258827fd84896402be3aecf3328484dd3d563ab9","tid":2143651,"uid":133,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"有創傷？邊度？個腦呀"},"citedBy":0,"repl